{
  "stem": "268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The name of the mine was also [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Laurahuette-- ?] two names.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was named after Laura.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He began to work in a coal mine during the German administration.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he worked for-- I believe he got a gold watch [INAUDIBLE] He [? worked, like, ?] 27 or 28 years in a coal mine until the outbreak of war-- of World War II.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was his profession.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He provided very well for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Coal miners in those days were paid very well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The living was above-- above the average worker because they were strongly unionized.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Polish, it was called 'spuka' and 'bratska,' which means the 'brotherhood of miners.' And he had tremendous benefits to the whole family, of course.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In school I never bought a book, a pencil.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Any kind of textbook, higher education, was provided by the coal mine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My relationship in my childhood-- my father was, to the-- to the best that I can recall--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a very warm relationship, the best I can remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, the nature of his work was such that we couldn't-- he worked, as I told you, in a coal mine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and he would work three shifts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then later on, he would work, like, two what they call swing shifts.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you worked the day shift, which means he was home by 3 or 4 o'clock, we could plan-- like, in the wintertime, he would take me sleigh riding.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember him pulling the sleigh and pushing me down the hill.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the summertime, he would take me to a soccer game.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I loved when he was working on the day shift.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
